title: Did MSNBC Play ‘You Complete Me’ Jerry Maguire Clip While Reporting on McCarthy’s Meeting With Trump?
subtitle: The clip was "pitch perfect satire," according to one guest.
author: Bethania Palma
vclaim: The MSNBC news and politics show "The 11th Hour with Brian Williams" cut to the famous "you complete me" scene from "Jerry Magure" instead of footage of a meeting between Kevin McCarthy and Donald Trump.
